<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3198] Change default Directory impl on 64bit linux to MMap</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3198</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Consistently in my NRT testing on Fedora 13 Linux, 64 bit JVM (Oracle 1.6.0_21) I see MMapDir getting better search and merge performance when compared to NIOFSDir.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think we should fix the default.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
